Web Scraper with Telegram Notifications

This Python application is designed to scrape content from a specified website, insert relevant information into a PostgreSQL database, and send notifications to a Telegram channel about newly added content.

Features

Web scraping of articles from a target website.
Insertion of scraped data into a PostgreSQL database.
Telegram notifications for newly added content.
Technologies Used

Python 3
Requests
BeautifulSoup
Psycopg2
Aiogram
Asyncio
PostgreSQL
Installation

Clone the repository:
bash
Copy code
git clone https://github.com/yourusername/web-scraper.git
Install dependencies using pip:
bash
Copy code
cd web-scraper
pip install -r requirements.txt
Set up a PostgreSQL database with appropriate tables. Ensure you have the necessary credentials.
Obtain a Telegram bot API token and configure a Telegram channel for receiving notifications.
Update the application code with the following configurations:
PostgreSQL database credentials
Telegram bot API token
Target website URL
Usage

Run the Python script to start scraping content:
Copy code
python scraper.py
The script will scrape the target website, insert new content into the database, and send notifications to the configured Telegram channel.
Ensure the script is run at appropriate intervals to keep the content updated.
